<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>ENOUGH | Tanya Hicks</title>
  <meta name="description" content="ENOUGH by Tanya Hicks. You were never the only thing that needed fixing." />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --pink: #E91D8C;
      --pink-dark: #C4106B;
      --purple: #6D4C9B;
      --teal: #4FCEC5;
      --teal-text: #2BA898;
      --gold: #C4A96A;
      --dark-text: #1A1A1A;
      --body-text: #3D3D3D;
      --muted: #7A7570;
      --bg-warm: #F5F1ED;
      --bg-white: #FFFFFF;
      --bg-light: #FAF8F6;
      --border: #E8E4DE;
    }
    * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    body { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; background: var(--bg-warm); color: var(--body-text); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; }

    .section { padding: clamp(72px, 10vw, 120px) clamp(20px, 5vw, 80px); }
    .section-warm { background: var(--bg-warm); }
    .section-white { background: var(--bg-white); }
    .section-dark { background: var(--dark-text); color: #fff; }
    .container-sm { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .container-md { max-width: 960px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .container-lg { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }

    .display-heading { font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: clamp(64px, 10vw, 120px); line-height: 1.05; color: var(--dark-text); }
    .section-heading { font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: clamp(32px, 4.5vw, 56px); line-height: 1.1; color: var(--dark-text); }
    .sub-heading { font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 28px); line-height: 1.2; color: var(--dark-text); }

    .eyebrow { display: block; font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 2.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--pink); margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .divider-line { width: 40px; height: 3px; background: var(--pink); margin-bottom: 16px; }

    .body-large { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: clamp(17px, 1.8vw, 20px); line-height: 1.75; color: var(--body-text); }
    .body-light { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-weight: 300; font-size: clamp(17px, 1.8vw, 20px); line-height: 1.75; color: var(--body-text); }
    .body { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--body-text); }
    .body-sm { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: var(--body-text); }
    .caption { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-weight: 400; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5; }

    .btn-primary { display: inline-block; background: var(--pink); color: #fff; border: none; border-radius: 8px; padding: 15px 32px; font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; cursor: pointer; transition: background 0.2s ease; text-decoration: none; }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--pink-dark); }
    .btn-secondary { display: inline-block; background: transparent; color: var(--purple); border: 2px solid var(--purple); border-radius: 8px; padding: 13px 28px; font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-weight: 600; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.5px; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s ease; text-decoration: none; }
    .btn-secondary:hover { background: var(--purple); color: #fff; }

    .btn-primary:focus-visible, .btn-secondary:focus-visible, a:focus-visible, input:focus-visible, button:focus-visible { outline: 2px solid var(--pink); outline-offset: 2px; }

    /* Nav */
    nav { position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; z-index: 100; background: rgba(245,241,237,0.95); backdrop-filter: blur(12px); padding: 16px clamp(20px, 5vw, 80px); display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    nav .nav-brand { font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-weight: 700; font-size: 22px; color: var(--dark-text); text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 3px; }
    nav .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 24px; list-style: none; }
    nav .nav-links a { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-weight: 500; font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--muted); text-decoration: none; transition: color 0.2s; }
    nav .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--dark-text); }
    @media (max-width: 768px) { nav .nav-links { display: none; } }

    /* Skip to content */
    .skip-link { position: absolute; top: -100px; left: 0; z-index: 9999; background: #fff; padding: 8px 16px; font-size: 14px; }
    .skip-link:focus { top: 0; }

    /* Scroll reveal */
    .reveal { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(28px); transition: opacity 0.75s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1), transform 0.75s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1); }
    .reveal.visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }

    /* Responsive hero grid */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      .hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
      .hero-grid > div:last-child { order: -1; margin-bottom: 24px; }
      .pillars-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    }

    /* ── Starting Line styles ── */
    #sl-root { width: 100%; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
    .sl-section-label { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--pink); text-align: center; margin-bottom: 2rem; opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px); transition: opacity 0.7s 0.2s ease, transform 0.7s 0.2s ease; }
    .sl-section-label.sl-visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    .sl-track-header { position: relative; width: 100%; margin-bottom: 0; }
    .sl-start-flag { position: absolute; left: 64%; transform: translateX(-50%); bottom: 0; font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: var(--gold); white-space: nowrap; text-align: center; line-height: 1; padding-bottom: 8px; }
    .sl-start-flag span { display: block; font-size: 0.62rem; font-weight: 500; color: rgba(196,169,106,0.65); letter-spacing: 0.12em; margin-top: 3px; }
    .sl-track-wrap {
      position: relative; width: 100%; height: 340px;
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, #e8f5e4 0%, #ddefd8 50%, #e8f5e4 100%);
      border-radius: 12px;
      border: 1.5px solid rgba(58,107,30,0.15);
      overflow: hidden;
      opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px);
      transition: opacity 0.7s 0.3s ease, transform 0.7s 0.3s ease;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 32px rgba(37,25,45,0.07);
    }
    .sl-track-wrap.sl-visible { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    .sl-lane-grid { position: absolute; inset: 0; background-image: repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, transparent 99px, rgba(109,76,155,0.07) 99px, rgba(109,76,155,0.07) 100px); pointer-events: none; }
    .sl-lane-line { position: absolute; left: 0; right: 0; height: 1px; background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, rgba(109,76,155,0.12) 15%, rgba(109,76,155,0.12) 85%, transparent); pointer-events: none; }
    .sl-startline { position: absolute; left: 64%; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 3px; background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 2%, var(--gold) 15%, var(--gold) 85%, transparent 98%); box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(196,169,106,0.35); pointer-events: none; }
    .sl-label-left { position: absolute; left: 20px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(37,25,45,0.25); letter-spacing: 2px; white-space: nowrap; pointer-events: none; }
    .sl-label-right { position: absolute; right: 20px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 10px; font-weight: 600; color: rgba(37,25,45,0.25); letter-spacing: 2px; pointer-events: none; }
    .sl-runner { position: absolute; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); cursor: pointer; z-index: 5; transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(.25,.46,.45,.94); }
    .sl-runner.is-active { z-index: 10; }
    .sl-runner-label { position: absolute; top: -58px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%); white-space: nowrap; text-align: center; transition: opacity 0.3s; }
    .sl-runner-label-main { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.2; }
    .sl-runner-label-sub { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.5px; margin-top: 3px; }
    .sl-bubble { border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: all 0.3s cubic-bezier(.25,.46,.45,.94); border: 2.5px solid; }
    .sl-icon-forward { display: inline-block; transform: scaleX(-1); }
    .sl-connector { position: absolute; left: 50%; top: 100%; transform: translateX(-50%); width: 2px; transition: opacity 0.3s; }
    .sl-prompt { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 0.75rem; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; text-align: center; margin-top: 1.4rem; opacity: 0; transition: opacity 0.6s 0.5s ease; }
    .sl-prompt.sl-visible { opacity: 1; }
    .sl-detail { max-width: 860px; margin: 2.5rem auto 0; }
    .sl-detail-card {
      border-radius: 18px; padding: 2.2rem 2.8rem;
      display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 2rem;
      animation: slSlideIn 0.35s cubic-bezier(.25,.46,.45,.94);
      background: var(--bg-light); border: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    @keyframes slSlideIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(12px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
    .sl-detail-icon { width: 68px; height: 68px; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 30px; flex-shrink: 0; border: 2.5px solid; }
    .sl-detail-tag { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 0.72rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 0.7rem; }
    .sl-detail-copy { font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-size: clamp(1.1rem, 2vw, 1.4rem); line-height: 1.6; color: var(--dark-text); margin: 0 0 0.9rem; font-style: italic; font-weight: 700; }
    .sl-detail-body { font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--muted); margin: 0; }


    /* ── MA interactive responsive ── */
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
      #book .container-md > div:first-child {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
      }
      #book .container-md img {
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      #ma-root > div:last-child {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr !important;
      }
      #ma-root [style*="grid-template-columns: repeat(6"] {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr) !important;
      }
      .sl-detail-card {
        flex-direction: column;
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }
    }
    @media (max-width: 480px) {
      #ma-root [style*="grid-template-columns: repeat(6"] {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr) !important;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<a href="#main" class="skip-link">Skip to content</a>
<nav>
  <a href="#" class="nav-brand">ENOUGH</a>
  <ul class="nav-links">
    <li><a href="#manifesto">Why</a></li>
    <li><a href="#feeling">Feeling</a></li>
    <li><a href="#book">Book</a></li>
    <li><a href="#stages">Stages</a></li>
    <li><a href="#speaking">Speaking</a></li>
  </ul>
</nav>

<main id="main">

<!-- SECTION 1 — HERO -->
<section class="section" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFFFFF 0%, #FFF0F8 50%, #F5F1ED 100%); padding-top: calc(clamp(72px, 10vw, 120px) + 80px); position: relative; overflow: hidden;">
  <div style="position: absolute; top: -100px; right: -100px; width: 600px; height: 600px; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(233,29,140,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%); pointer-events: none; z-index: 0;"></div>
  <div class="container-lg hero-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 340px; gap: clamp(32px, 5vw, 64px); align-items: center; position: relative; z-index: 1;">
    <div>
      <span class="eyebrow">The Misfit Matriarch</span>
      <h1 class="display-heading" style="margin-bottom: 16px;">Enough<span style="color: #E91D8C;">.</span></h1>
      <p class="sub-heading" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-weight: 400; font-style: italic; color: var(--body-text); margin-bottom: 24px;">One word. Four truths.<br>You already know which one brought you here.</p>
      <p class="body-light" style="max-width: 520px;">You have worked too hard for life to still be this hard. You tried the therapy. The routines. The boundaries. The books. And you are still exhausted in ways that none of it explains. That is not a you problem. Nobody ever showed you what you were actually working with. Every strategy you were handed was built for someone else. It was not bad faith. It was the wrong map. This book is the right one.</p>
      <p style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 15px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 32px;">Misfits don't fit the mould. They forge it.</p>
      <div style="margin-top: 32px; display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <a href="#book" class="btn-primary">Pre-order ENOUGH</a>
        <a href="#manifesto" class="btn-secondary">Read on &#8595;</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div style="position: relative;">
      <img src="assets/WCW Paris Eiffel Tower Picnic 2025-151_edited.jpg" alt="Tanya Hicks" style="width: clamp(280px, 28vw, 420px); height: clamp(320px, 32vw, 480px); object-fit: cover; object-position: center top; border-radius: 0; display: block; mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,1) 40%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 100%), linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0,0,0,0) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,1) 15%, rgba(0,0,0,1) 85%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 100%); -webkit-mask-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, rgba(0,0,0,1) 40%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 100%), linear-gradient(to right, rgba(0,0,0,0) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,1) 15%, rgba(0,0,0,1) 85%, rgba(0,0,0,0) 100%); mask-composite: intersect; -webkit-mask-composite: source-in;" />
    </div>
  </div>
  <div style="max-width: 1100px; margin: 48px auto 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); padding-top: 24px;">
    <p style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 0.3px;">Matriarch. Viking. Misfit. Clinician. Scholar. Human. Birther of the Enduring. Author of ENOUGH.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SECTION 2 — MANIFESTO -->
<section class="section section-white" id="manifesto">
  <div class="container-sm">
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
    <span class="eyebrow">Why this book exists</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">You were never the only thing that needed fixing.</h2>
    <p class="body-light" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">You are not lazy. You are not weak. You are not bad at being a person. You are running on half your energy before the day even starts, and nobody has ever shown you where the rest of it is going.</p>
    <p class="body-light" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">Every strategy. Every protocol. Every try harder. Aimed at you. As if you were the thing that needed fixing.</p>
    <p class="body-light">You were never the only thing that needed fixing. And you have had enough of not knowing what the rest of it actually is.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SECTION 3 — YOU KNOW THIS FEELING -->
<section class="section" id="feeling" style="background: #FFF0F8;">
  <div class="container-sm">
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
    <span class="eyebrow">You know this feeling</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading" style="margin-bottom: 40px;">Both of those things can be true.</h2>
    <div style="border-left: 2px solid var(--pink); padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <p style="font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--body-text);">You are in the meeting. You are performing fine. Your body left twenty minutes ago.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="border-left: 2px solid var(--pink); padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <p style="font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--body-text);">Rest does not bring you back. It just makes the gap quieter.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="border-left: 2px solid var(--pink); padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <p style="font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--body-text);">You know what to do. You cannot sustain doing it.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="border-left: 2px solid var(--pink); padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <p style="font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--body-text);">You compare yourself to someone who manages the same load with less cost, and you cannot work out what you are doing wrong.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="border-left: 2px solid var(--pink); padding-left: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      <p style="font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--body-text);">You lay on the floor at the end of a day that should not have been that hard, wondering what is wrong with you.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="border-left: 2px solid var(--purple); padding-left: 20px;">
      <p style="font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--dark-text); font-style: italic;">The thing that needed fixing was never just you.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SECTION 4 — STARTING LINE -->
<section class="section section-white" id="starting-line">
  <div class="container-md">
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
    <span class="eyebrow">What nobody told you</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">Not everyone starts from the same starting line.</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--body-text); max-width: 640px; margin-bottom: 40px;">Before you spend more on the next course, the next coach, the next strategy — do you actually have your feet in the starting blocks? Or are you still making your way across the car park?</p>

    <div style="border-radius: 12px; overflow: visible; border: 1px solid var(--border); margin: 40px 0; background: var(--bg-warm); padding: 32px 28px; width: 100vw; margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%); border-radius: 0; border-left: none; border-right: none;">
      <div id="sl-root">
        <div class="sl-section-label" id="sl-section-label">Where your starting line actually is</div>
        <div class="sl-track-header" style="height:38px;">
          <div class="sl-start-flag">START<span>assumed equal</span></div>
        </div>
        <div class="sl-track-wrap" id="sl-track-wrap">
          <div class="sl-lane-grid"></div>
          <div class="sl-lane-line" style="top:33%"></div>
          <div class="sl-lane-line" style="top:55%"></div>
          <div class="sl-lane-line" style="top:77%"></div>
          <div class="sl-startline"></div>
          <div class="sl-label-left">&larr; NOT EVEN ON THE TRACK</div>
          <div class="sl-label-right">FINISH &rarr;</div>
          <div id="sl-runners-mount"></div>
        </div>
        <p class="sl-prompt" id="sl-prompt">&uarr; tap any runner to read their starting line</p>
        <div class="sl-detail" id="sl-detail"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p style="font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--body-text); max-width: 640px; margin-top: 40px;">The advice you were given was built for someone else's starting position. Someone else's nervous system. Someone else's load. It was not bad faith. It was the wrong map. Nobody asked where your actual starting line was. Enough of running someone else's race. ENOUGH is the first honest map of the one you are actually running.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SECTION 5 — THREE PILLARS -->
<section class="section section-warm" id="pillars">
  <div class="container-md">
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
    <span class="eyebrow">What this book shows you</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">Here is what ENOUGH actually does.</h2>
    <div class="pillars-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); gap: 24px;">
      <div style="background: var(--bg-white); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 32px; border-top: 3px solid #E91D8C;">
        <span style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--pink);">Where your energy is actually going</span>
        <p class="body" style="margin-top: 12px;">The invisible costs that drain you before your day begins. The ones no blood test, no therapist, no morning routine has ever named. Enough of paying costs you cannot even see.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--bg-white); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 32px; border-top: 3px solid #6D4C9B;">
        <span style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--purple);">How you were actually built</span>
        <p class="body" style="margin-top: 12px;">Your nervous system. Your wiring. Not the version you have been performing. The real one. And why it was never the deficit.</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background: var(--bg-white); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 32px; border-top: 3px solid #4FCEC5;">
        <span style="font-weight: 600; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--teal-text);">What to do with what you know</span>
        <p class="body" style="margin-top: 12px;">Not try harder. Not push through. Four precise moves that work with your design instead of against it.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SECTION 6 — BOOK -->
<section class="section section-white" id="book">
  <div class="container-md">
    <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr auto; gap: clamp(32px, 5vw, 64px); align-items: start;">
      <div>
        <div class="divider-line"></div>
        <span class="eyebrow">The book</span>
        <h2 class="section-heading" style="margin-bottom: 24px; color: #E91D8C;">ENOUGH</h2>
        <p class="body-light" style="font-size: 19px; margin-bottom: 24px;">This is the book that explains why you are this tired.</p>
        <p style="font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--body-text); margin-bottom: 24px;">Not the tired that sleep fixes. The tired that borrows from your patience, your creativity, your hope, and spends it all on getting through a Tuesday. This book shows you where the drain is, what it has cost you, and what becomes possible when you stop fighting your own design and start building from it.</p>
        <div style="border-left: 3px solid var(--gold); padding-left: 20px; margin: 32px 0;">
          <p style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', Georgia, serif; font-style: italic; font-size: 17px; color: var(--body-text);">Written for the people who kept going. The ones who did the work, held it together, and are still here. The enduring.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="#closing" class="btn-primary" style="margin-top: 32px;">Pre-order ENOUGH &rarr;</a>
      </div>
      <img src="assets/Book cover.png" alt="ENOUGH by Tanya Hicks" style="width: clamp(160px, 18vw, 240px); border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 20px 56px rgba(233,29,140,0.2), 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); flex-shrink: 0;" />
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SECTION 7 — SIX STAGES -->
<section class="section section-warm" id="stages">
  <div class="container-md">
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
    <span class="eyebrow">The architecture behind the book</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading" style="margin-bottom: 24px;">Six stages. One race. Your design.</h2>
    <div style="display: flex; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; margin-bottom: 32px;">
      <span style="font-weight: 500; font-size: 13px; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px; background: var(--bg-white); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--body-text);">Recognition</span>
      <span style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px;">&rarr;</span>
      <span style="font-weight: 500; font-size: 13px; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px; background: var(--bg-white); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--body-text);">Clarity</span>
      <span style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px;">&rarr;</span>
      <span style="font-weight: 500; font-size: 13px; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px; background: var(--bg-white); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--body-text);">Acceptance</span>
      <span style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px;">&rarr;</span>
      <span style="font-weight: 500; font-size: 13px; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px; background: var(--bg-white); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--body-text);">Intervention</span>
      <span style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px;">&rarr;</span>
      <span style="font-weight: 500; font-size: 13px; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px; background: var(--bg-white); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--body-text);">Alignment</span>
      <span style="color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px;">&rarr;</span>
      <span style="font-weight: 500; font-size: 13px; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 20px; background: var(--bg-white); border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--body-text);">Sustainability</span>
    </div>
    <div style="background: var(--bg-white); border-radius: 12px; border: 1px solid var(--border); overflow: hidden;">
      <div id="ma-root" style="padding: clamp(1.2rem, 4vw, 2.5rem);"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SECTION 8 — ABOUT -->
<section class="section section-white" id="about">
  <div class="container-sm">
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
    <span class="eyebrow">About Tanya</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">This work was not built as theory first.</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--body-text); margin-bottom: 24px;">It was built on snapped ligaments, sensory overwhelm, a brain that could not understand instruction manuals written in typical language, and a heart that broke over and over again.</p>
    <p style="font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--body-text); margin-bottom: 24px;">And then I had a daughter who was built like me. And I decided: not on my watch.</p>
    <p style="font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--body-text);">What came next was forged in clinical practice, neurodivergent-affirming support, community design, leadership, and advocacy, until a framework emerged that actually worked, for people who were never the whole problem.</p>
    <p style="font-weight: 500; font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 32px; padding-top: 24px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);">Matriarch. Viking. Misfit. Clinician. Scholar. Human. Birther of the Enduring. Author of ENOUGH.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SECTION 9 — SPEAKING -->
<section class="section" id="speaking" style="background: #FFF0F8;">
  <div class="container-sm">
    <img src="assets/WCW 2025 d1-152_edited.jpg" alt="Tanya Hicks speaking" style="width: 100%; max-width: 720px; height: clamp(200px, 28vw, 360px); object-fit: cover; object-position: center 20%; border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 40px; display: block;" />
    <div class="divider-line"></div>
    <span class="eyebrow">Speaking</span>
    <h2 class="section-heading" style="margin-bottom: 32px;">If capable people keep struggling in your system, the problem is probably not the people.</h2>
    <p style="font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--body-text); margin-bottom: 24px;">Good intentions do not prevent harm. When you cannot see the full load someone is carrying, you cannot give them what they actually need, no matter how much you want to help.</p>
    <p style="font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.8; color: var(--body-text); margin-bottom: 32px;">First, understand what it costs them to be here. Be the coach the person in front of you actually needs. Not the coach you were trained to be for someone else.</p>
    <a href="mailto:hello@tanyahicks.com" class="btn-secondary">Speaking enquiries &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>

