    <span style="font: 400 13px 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; color: #7A7570; letter-spacing: 0.2px;">2025 Honourable Mention · Thought Leader · WCW APAC</span>
    <span style="font: 400 13px 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; color: #7A7570; letter-spacing: 0.2px;">·</span>
    <span style="font: 400 13px 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; color: #7A7570; letter-spacing: 0.2px;">2026 Finalist · Community Group of the Year · SC Australia Day Awards</span>
    <span style="font: 400 13px 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; color: #7A7570; letter-spacing: 0.2px;">·</span>
    <span style="font: 400 13px 'Inter', -apple-system, sans-serif; color: #7A7570; letter-spacing: 0.2px;">2026 Finalist · Citizen of the Year · SC Australia Day Awards</span>
